usdOspfAgent.contactinfo: Unisphere Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@UnisphereNetworks.com
usdOspfAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the Open Shortest Path First (OSPF) routing protocol component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Routing Switch family of products.

usdOspfAgentV1.name: usdOspfAgentV1
usdOspfAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the OSPF component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the OSPF component was supported in the
        Unisphere RX 2.x and 3.x system releases.
usdOspfAgentV1.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the OSPF application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when new objects were added to the usdOspfBasicGroup.

usdOspfAgentV2.name: usdOspfAgentV2
usdOspfAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the OSPF component of the Unisphere Routing Switch SNMP
        agent.  This version of the OSPF component is supported in the Unisphere
        RX 4.0 and subsequent system releases.
usdOspfAgentV2.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the OSPF application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
